{"id":651413,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":4,"day":15}],"page":"2","source":"《文汇月刊》","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"140","ytitle":"","mtitle":"路卡","ftitle":"——并非讽刺交通民警","authors":["陈显荣"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁聪　画　陈显荣　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身坐交通亭，管开红绿灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面车辆来，鸣笛要通行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让过不让过，看你灵不灵:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要送上礼，马上开绿灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要先“表示”，红灯最无情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消防救火车，无贿也得停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喇叭震天响，权当耳朵聋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不留买路钱，休想过岗亭!(原载《文汇月刊》今年第四期)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1983\\04\\834F021001.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>丁聪</FONT>"}]}